When she was given 12 months to live, Kim Ferguson was not the kind of person who was destined to 'sit at home and die', as she said in her own words.

Instead she decided to make her way through her battle with cancer 'one outfit at a time'.

With the help of her two loving daughters Kim started up an Instagram account to document her outfits, putting her love for fashion and her zest for life on show to inspire herself, and others. 

