Kim's journey began more than a decade ago when she was diagnosed with colorectal cancer which meant she underwent three 'quite full-on operations'.

Doctors were shocked that someone who lived such a healthy lifestyle - Kim is passionate about yoga, swimming, and has always been a vegetarian and light drinker - could develop such a disease.

