However 24 hours later the Ferguson's' world was turned upside down again when they were told Kim was so unwell that 90 percent of the organs below her waist had to be removed.

'I have no bowel, no bladder, only part of my stomach, I had organs removed I didn't even know I had.'

This was around the point the 57-year-old started her Instagram, as an outlet for herself but which quickly turned into a support network for others.

