Although it has been more than 365 days since her initial diagnosis, the central coast woman - who spends much of her time at the beach or in the water - said for her the days she documents is about when she feels most herself.

When asked what she'll do when she makes it to the final day in her countdown, Kim couldn't contain her excitement.

'I'm going to have a party! A big party like fashion week,' she laughed. 

